mods.abstract: A black and white full-length portrait of Bobby Greenwood and Jack Wall, P.G.A. Pros and Benchcraft Golf Seminar instructors, kneeling with their golf bags in front of a Benchcraft informational sign. A Rubylith masking film is taped to the photo. A typed note on the back of the photo says, "Benchcraft 4/82."
